{
  "info": {
    "name": "GateBuddy API",
    "description": "Comprehensive API for GateBuddy - The Intelligent Airport Companion Ecosystem.\n\n**Main API URL:** http://localhost:3001/api/v1/\n**Recommendation Service:** http://localhost:8000/\n\n**Authentication:** Use `Bearer {{token}}` in the Authorization header for protected endpoints.\n\n## Core Ecosystem Features\n1. **Unified OAuth 2.0**: Integrated Google, Facebook, and GitHub sign-in.\n2. **IATA 791 Standard**: Boarding pass scanning with Julian date validation.\n3. **AI Concierge**: Google Gemini-powered chatbot for terminal assistance.\n4. **Live Scraper**: Python-based real-time destination tips.\n5. **Indoor Maps**: GeoJSON support for Gates, Lounges, and Retail.\n6. **FCM Notifications**: Firebase Cloud Messaging for real-time alerts.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
